    '9':  { standard: "Jupiter is at home here — philosophy, travel, and meaning-making arrive abundantly. The world is genuinely large for you.", oracle: "Jupiter in its home sign expands ideology and the sense of being right. Dogmatism and the overconfidence of the explorer are the structural excesses." },
