    '13': { standard: "Expansion arrives through the unnamed and the unconventional. Growth for you looks different than the standard map describes.", oracle: "Jupiter in the thirteenth house amplifies unconventional growth trajectories. The expansion is into what doesn't have a category yet; this is genuinely productive and structurally confusing." },
