    '7':  { standard: "Partnership carries an element of the transcendent or the sacrificial. What you seek in relationship is partly divine and partly impossible.", oracle: "Neptune in the seventh house dissolves relational clarity. The partner is idealized; the actual person is obscured by the projection of what the self needs them to be." },
    '8':  { standard: "Transformation, shared power, and depth carry a spiritual or dissolving quality. What dies in you does not always leave a clean line.", oracle: "Neptune in the eighth house dissolves the boundary between the self and what it merges with. Psychological dissolution is a structural feature of intimate encounters; boundaries are unclear." },
    '9':  { standard: "Philosophy and spirituality are genuine and sustaining. The search for meaning carries real depth and real permeability.", oracle: "Neptune in the ninth house dissolves ideological clarity. Belief and fantasy are difficult to distinguish; spiritual seeking is real and structurally prone to manipulation." },
