    '11': { standard: "The collective vision is genuine and idealistic. The communities you join carry something of the transcendent.", oracle: "Neptune in the eleventh house dissolves collective clarity. Groups become sites of idealization and disillusionment; the community is often not what it appears to be." },
    '12': { standard: "Neptune is at home in the twelfth — the interior life is rich, spiritual, and vast. The inner world is real even when invisible.", oracle: "Neptune in its home house amplifies unconscious dissolution. The inner life is maximally permeable to spiritual and collective content; the boundary between self and ocean is structurally thin." },
    '13': { standard: "The dissolving principle operates in the unnamed territory. What is unclear in you is located at the threshold — neither in nor out.", oracle: "Neptune in the thirteenth house dissolves the unnamed. What is already the least structured territory in the chart loses even more definition; this is either mystical resource or structural confusion." },
